{"tid":581884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★機械臂+VR橋本環奈「餵」你食糖！","createTime":"2018-03-05T16:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T07:03:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a72b25a112b821f88ee320fd849b2e7126b85860","tid":581884,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:54:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lpsjg-PoSJo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dlpsjg-PoSJo&d=9WSmceSPMME4aK%2F%2FDjvC4AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=44403c62\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lpsjg-PoSJo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://puccho.jp/a-n/img/main_img.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuccho.jp%2Fa-n%2Fimg%2Fmain_img.jpg&h=5ce1d62b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本女星橋本環奈被譽為「千年一遇美少女」，在各地都有不少支持者。最近，日本糖果公司 UHA味覺糖在 旗下產品 Puccho 的社交媒體帳號 Twitter 上舉辦活動，讓橋本環奈的支持者透過附機械臂的虛擬實境（VR）眼罩，讓橋本環奈「餵」支持者們吃糖果。<br />\n<br />\n活動所用的 VR 眼罩附有機械臂，配合 VR 影片中穿著高中生制服的橋本環奈，將糖果送到用家口中。眼罩內裝有 3 種不同的VR影片，當中更包括在快要吃到糖果時突然抽手的假動作影片，讓用家可藉此嚐到甘甜的青春滋味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/4-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F4-2.jpg&h=c1188d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/5-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F5-1.jpg&h=a055e14f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/6-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F6-2.jpg&h=c5ed5daf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/03/05/hashimoto-kanna-vr/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2Fhashimoto-kanna-vr%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=9WSmceSPMME4aK%2F%2FDjvC4AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=0e45540d\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/03/05/hashimoto-kanna-vr/fun-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://puccho.jp/a-n/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuccho.jp%2Fa-n%2F&d=9WSmceSPMME4aK%2F%2FDjvC4AhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c235fae2\" target=\"_blank\">http://puccho.jp/a-n/</a>"},{"pid":"6184a49b3e64caa1ae42b964ca0f77a63c79720d","tid":581884,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea21ba0b35765f303390195f248909f8fcdedead","tid":581884,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"幾時可以機械手打J"},{"pid":"2da609a1beea8c24eed7ba9e07bf96db523e552d","tid":581884,"uid":91931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:59:18.000Z","msg":"睇圖都笑撚死"},{"pid":"90a5d800d958dd6802d7eed94a77f321b692f4b7","tid":581884,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T17:02:49.000Z","msg":"可唔可以換支假陽具"},{"pid":"7441068bea3d1d03926bbb189f79f56ba840a929","tid":581884,"uid":90,"like":14,"dislike":6,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T17:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/e/eb/S4_545afd334e6fe.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/400?cb=20150910043757\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fe%2Feb%2FS4_545afd334e6fe.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F400%3Fcb%3D20150910043757&h=2bfd2f5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afa02b01a000eac1f6fc09f309798d9f1d02ad5c","tid":581884,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,